{
  "texts": [
    "• Seamless Integration with User Journey: Recommendations are integrated into various stages of the user's journey on the platform, from home page displays to targeted email campaigns.",
    "• Privacy and Data Security: Ensuring user data privacy and security is paramount, with strict adherence to data protection regulations.",
    "• Bias and Fairness: The system continuously monitors for and mitigates biases in recommendations, ensuring a fair and diverse range of product suggestions.",
    "• Algorithmic Transparency: Maintaining a level of transparency in how recommendations are generated to avoid the 'black box' effect and build user trust.",
    "Part III: Search Engine-Based Recommendations for New E-commerce Platforms"
  ]
}